Interface MutableDistribution

All Known Subinterfaces:
DoubleArrayContainer, IntArrayContainer
public interface MutableDistribution

Marker interface for classes that represent distributions of some kind, and that can be altered. In particular, marks distribution classes that can be processed by a DistributionProcessor.
